# NuGet
project.lock.json
project.fragment.lock.json
# Root-anchored: the .NET SDK's build-output `artifacts/` dir only. WITHOUT the leading
# slash this also matched the source folder src/.../Services/Workflows/Artifacts/ and silently
# kept IArtifactStore.cs & siblings out of git, breaking clean-checkout builds.
/artifacts/

